translations: 无与伦比的；不等同的，不能比拟的

sentences.sentence: The camera combines rugged reliability with unequalled optical performance and speed.
sentences.translation: 这款照相机集经久可靠性、无与伦比的光学性能和速度于一身。

sentences.sentence: This record figure was unequalled for 13 years.
In time, he gave a vivid, perhaps unequalled, account of an artist making art.
sentences.translation: 随着时间的推移，他展现了作为一位创造型艺术家的栩栩如生、也许是无与伦比的记叙[才华]。
